=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; }
        .email-wrapper { background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 30px 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #4f46e5 100%); padding: 25px 30px; }
        .header h1 { color: #ffffff; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0; }
        .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px; }
        .content { padding: 35px 30px; }
        .content p { color: #333333; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .data-box { background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 3px solid #6366f1; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .data-row { margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .data-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
        .data-label { color: #666666; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .data-value { color: #333333; font-size: 15px; }
        .status-badge { display: inline-block; background-color: #eef2ff; color: #4338ca; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
        .cta-button { display: inline-block; background-color: #6366f1; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .footer { background-color: #fafafa; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8; }
        .footer p { margin: 3px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #999999; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>🔍 Inspección Enviada a Revisión</h1>
                <p>Un agente ha completado un informe de inspección</p>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Se ha recibido un informe de inspección para revisión. Por favor, revísalo y envíalo al propietario cuando esté listo.</p>
                <div class="data-box">
                    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Agente</span><span class="data-value">{{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.agent.name }}</span></div>
                    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Correo del Agente</span><span class="data-value">{{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.agent.email }}</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="data-box">
                    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Propiedad</span><span class="data-value">{{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.inspection.address }}</span></div>
                    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Propietario</span><span class="data-value">{{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.inspection.owner_name || 'No registrado' }}</span></div>
                    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Arrendatario</span><span class="data-value">{{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.inspection.tenant_name || 'No registrado' }}</span></div>
                    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Fecha de Inspección</span><span class="data-value">{{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.inspection.inspection_date || 'No indicada' }}</span></div>
                    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Estado</span><span class="status-badge">En Revisión</span></div>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align: center;"><a href="{{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.inspection.url }}" class="cta-button">Revisar Inspección →</a></div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer"><p><strong>RE/MAX Exclusive Chile</strong></p><p>Sistema automático de notificaciones</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
